about.projectDescription: DAMAC Bay at Dubai Harbour is a masterpiece of luxury living by DAMAC Properties, featuring exquisite seafront residences with interiors by Cavalli. These elegant apartments offer breathtaking skyline views, while the exclusive amenities create an unparalleled living experience. With the launch of DAMAC Bay Phase 2, even more opulent options are available, including super-luxury duplexes with private pools, all within a stunning 49-storey tower.

amenities.text: DAMAC Bay offers a wealth of world-class amenities designed to elevate luxury living. Nature-inspired designs blend seamlessly with contemporary luxury, offering serene spaces surrounded by greenery and waterfront views. The development also features floating relaxation pods, infinity pools, wellness centers, and climate-controlled environments, creating a harmonious balance between comfort, well-being, and natural beauty.

Our installment schemas are devoid of any latent charges or unanticipated costs.
A 4% DLD (Dubai Land Department) fee applies to all real estate transactions in Dubai and must be paid in addition to the property's purchase price.

DAMAC Properties, a key part of DAMAC Group since 1982, has been a major player in the Middle East's luxury real estate market. Known for its iconic residential, commercial, and leisure properties, DAMAC enhances cityscapes with its diverse portfolio of skyscrapers, communities, and branded residences.
